    <abstract>
      <t>This document proposes a Lightweight DHCPv6 Relay Agent (LDRA) that is used to insert relay agent options in DHCPv6 message exchanges identifying client-facing interfaces. The LDRA can be implemented in existing access nodes (such as DSLAMs and Ethernet switches) that do not support IPv6 control or routing functions.</t>
